description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A FRESH START OR A CLEAN BREAK?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why not consider becoming a Consultant Psychiatrist in in the county of Cornwall? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Due to expansion and retirement we have a range of current opportunities to join our medical teams in Adult Psychiatry and CAMHS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is an opportunity to practise psychiatry in a forward looking organisation, within a beautiful rural county with a rich and diverse landscape, wide open spaces and vibrant communities of villages and small towns. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;So why come and work with us at CFT?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a cohesive and collaborative senior medical group. We enjoy a range of academic opportunities through links with Exeter and Plymouth Universities and have an excellent local CPD programme. We work in a continuity model of care and protect our SPAs. We have a learning culture, with high trainee satisfaction and exam success. We support flexible working and job sharing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;And why come to live and work in Cornwall? &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our great work/life balance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The fascinating history, culture, natural environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outstanding education providers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We live in strong, healthy communities&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Airport and rail, including sleeper trains link us to the UK and Europe&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We enjoy a fabulous landscape for surfing, sailing, hiking, biking&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent food is available, from Michelin restaurants to local markets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did we mention superb beaches?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or to arrange an informal visit, please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
